ed loop that reads all matching events (~27M for tracker events)\nbefore applying the org unit filter late via the joined organisationunit table.\n\nAdd ev.organisationunitid in (:evOrgUnits) directly to the WHERE clause for\nSELECTED mode in both tracker events and single events. This gives PG an early\npredicate on the event row itself, enabling it to avoid the full index scan.\nConfirmed: 173,701ms -\u003e 14ms for tracker events, 9,601ms -\u003e ~14ms for single events.","author":{"name":"teleivo","email":"teleivo@users.noreply.github.com"},"id":"9c05b2f22e73895da9f78ab6961c7d7cd15fd8c2","tree_id":"1247efb2b513f6dd76d6ce7dcfdb26b4cd364cc4","timestamp":"2026-03-05T10:38:31Z","committer":{"name":"teleivo","email":"teleivo@users.noreply.github.com"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains the service layer and Web API.","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-